steps.name: Diego visits https://www.saucedemo.com/
Diego waits up to 10 seconds using visibility_of_element_located with [login button]
Diego logs in into saucelabs.com
Diego enters "standard_user" into the username input.
Diego enters "secret_sauce" into the password input.
Diego clicks on the login button.
Diego buy some products
Diego waits up to 10 seconds using visibility_of_element_located with [add to cart backpag button]
Diego add some product to the cart
Diego clicks on the add to cart backpag button.
Diego add some product to the cart
Diego clicks on the add to cart light button.
Diego clicks on the shopping cart button.
Diego waits up to 10 seconds using visibility_of_element_located with [checkout button]
Diego clicks on the checkout button.
Diego waits up to 10 seconds using visibility_of_element_located with [continue button]
Diego complete the checkout form
Diego enters "Bill Bowers" into the firts name input.
Diego enters "Stevens" into the last name input.
Diego enters "42030" into the zip input.
Diego clicks on the continue button.
Diego waits up to 10 seconds using visibility_of_element_located with [finish button]
Diego clicks on the finish button.
Diego waits up to 10 seconds using visibility_of_element_located with [complete order text]
Diego sees if the confirm order text is 'Thank you for your order!', verbatim.
Diego reads the confirm order text
=> 'Thank you for your order!'
... hoping it's 'Thank you for your order!', verbatim.
=> an object with str 'Thank you for your order!'
